This folder contains code for the following components:
1. Clustering and characterization of the galaxy data, as illustrated in Section 3.2 (MBC-GAMAData.R);
2. The MtFAD-q algorithm, described in Sections 2.1 and 2.2 (mtfad.R);
3. A 3D visualization function for simple clusters, discussed in Section 3.2.1 (starcoord3d.R);
4. A pairwise overlap map function, described in Section 3.2.3 (utilis.R);
5. A GDT function for composite clusters, described in Section 3.2.3 (Gtrans-sync.R).
